# Free form handler (Web3Forms) — used by the "On demand" and "Tenders" forms.
# The access key is PUBLIC (it ships in the page HTML), but is kept in an env var
# so it is easy to rotate / set per environment.
#
# 1. Create a free key at https://web3forms.com (enter the inbox email, e.g. info@teranovagroup.com).
# 2. In Cloudflare Pages → project → Settings → Environment variables, add:
#       PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY = <your access key>   (for Production and Preview)
# 3. Re-deploy.
PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
